title: (c) and (d) of the Dublin Docklands Development Authority (Dissolution) Act
heading: 2. The Dublin Docklands Development Authority (Dissolution) Act, 2015
text_raw:
2. The Dublin Docklands Development Authority (Dissolution) Act, 2015 
(Docklands Oversight and Consultative Forum - Prescribed Bodies) Order 
2016 is amended ̶ 

(a) 

by substituting for subparagraph 3(e) the following: 

“(e) Docklands Financial Services Group”, 

(b) by inserting after subparagraph 5(f) the following: 

“(g) Office of Public Works”. 

GIVEN under my Official Seal, 

14 May, 2024. 

DARRAGH O’BRIEN, 

Minister for Housing, Local Government and Heritage. 

Notice of the making of this Statutory Instrument was published in 
"Iris Oifigiúil" of 17th May, 2024.
